text: Lasianthus wallacei is a species of plant in the family Rubiaceae. It is endemic to Tanzania. ==Sources== * Lovett, J. & Clarke, G.P. 1998. Lasianthus wallacei. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 22 August 2007.
